      "Develop an adaptive routing algorithm that adjusts based on curvature diagnostics, comparing it to baseline static routing methods.",
      "Conduct experiments across various datasets (e.g., MNIST, CIFAR-10) to assess generalization performance, computational efficiency, and robustness against perturbations.",
      "Use formal PAC-Bayes generalization bounds to quantify performance improvements, with multi-seed variance quantification to ensure reproducibility."
