      "The method's performance may vary depending on the model architecture and dataset characteristics.",
      "Strict adherence to latency budgets may limit the model's flexibility in dynamic environments."
    ]
  }
}
``` 

This refined proposal emphasizes the innovative integration of PAC-Bayes and Jacobian-based methods, clearly delineating its contribution while remaining feasible within an academic research context. It is designed to align closely with the outlined methodological preferences while targeting high-impact outcomes.
