To carve out a unique niche, I propose integrating training-free mechanisms with an emphasis on a mathematically grounded evaluation of quantization strategies, leveraging curvature-aware optimization and geometric diagnostics. This would further distinguish the project from existing paradigms by focusing on not just efficiency, but also the theoretical underpinnings that govern the performance of these quantization strategies.

Here’s a refined proposal:

