    "Related Work": "Existing research on mixed-precision inference primarily focuses on static optimization or heuristic methods that lack adaptability to dynamic input distributions. Recent works like Spectral Latent Steering and Spectral Quantization Routing offer insight into geometric approaches but do not fully leverage curvature diagnostics for real-time routing decisions. This proposal aims to bridge this gap by integrating curvature-aware strategies into a dynamic routing framework.",
