      "4. Analyze the impact of varying latency budgets on model performance to identify the Pareto frontier between throughput and accuracy."
    ],
    "Risk Factors and Limitations": [
      "The effectiveness of the Jacobian-based approach may vary across different architectures and tasks, limiting generalizability.",
      "Potential trade-offs between accuracy and resource savings may not be acceptable for all applications.",
      "Layer skipping may introduce instability in model performance, requiring careful calibration of thresholds."
    ]
  }
}
``` 

