      "Experiment 3: Measure the accuracy, latency, and memory usage of the proposed method compared to existing approaches, focusing on achieving a Pareto-optimal balance between throughput and accuracy."
    ],
    "Risk Factors and Limitations": "Potential risks include the challenge of ensuring that the spectral analysis accurately reflects the quantization sensitivity of layers in a diverse set of models. Limitations may arise from the reliance on specific model architectures, and there may be difficulty in generalizing findings across all types of neural networks."
