This refined proposal emphasizes the innovative angle of training-free optimization proxies based on curvature, aims for empirical validation, and maintains a rigorous approach to evaluating the proposed methodologies. It integrates aspects of existing literature while carving out a unique niche focused on explicit curvature diagnostics and stability metrics.
