5. **Integration of Multi-Faceted Metrics**: This proposal can integrate a comprehensive set of metrics that account for perturbation costs, memory bandwidth, and throughput-accuracy trade-offs, thus providing a more holistic understanding of the performance implications of the proposed mechanism.

With these insights, the refined proposal will be structured as follows:

