    "Risk Factors and Limitations": [
      "The geometric properties may not hold consistently across all architectures, limiting the generalizability of the approach.",
      "Potential challenges in accurately quantifying curvature and distribution characteristics can affect the effectiveness of the proposed method.",
      "The reliance on deterministic methods may lead to suboptimal performance in highly dynamic or complex model architectures."
    ]
  }
}
```

### Reflection
1. **Quality**: The proposal presents a unique and rigorous approach to mixed-precision quantization that diverges from existing heuristic-based methodologies. By anchoring the framework in geometric properties, it aligns well with the research context of training-free representation geometry.
  
