    "Related Work": "Existing approaches like LithOS and Unified Operator Fusion target static optimizations for GPU resource management and kernel fusion, but do not leverage real-time profiling to adapt kernel implementations dynamically. This proposal aims to fill that gap by utilizing runtime profiling data to inform adaptive kernel specialization.",
