      "3. A/B Testing: Conduct A/B tests comparing traditional fixed-precision KV caches against our adaptive framework under varying load conditions to assess improvements in latency and throughput.",
      "4. Energy Efficiency Measurements: Measure the energy consumption associated with adaptive quantization versus traditional methods to quantify potential gains in energy efficiency."
